codeGet:
select 
    rbrcomp_aidy_code,
    rbrcomp_amt,
    mil_ben,
    service_code,
    service_desc,
    pct,
    to_char(floor(nvl(rbrcomp_amt*pct,0)), '99G999G999G999', 'NLS_NUMERIC_CHARACTERS=",."') tuition_benefit,
    to_char(floor(nvl((case when mil_ben = 'CH33' then 5066*pct 
                            when service_code = '2' then 1722 
                            when service_code = 3 then 2122
                            when mil_ben = 'CH1606' then 397
                            when mil_ben = 'VRE' then 605
                            when mil_ben = 'DEA' then 1265
                        end),0)), '99G999G999G999', 'NLS_NUMERIC_CHARACTERS=",."') housing_allowance,
    to_char(floor(nvl((case when mil_ben = 'CH33' then 1000*pct
                            when mil_ben = 'VRE' then 1971
                            end),0)), '99G999G999G999', 'NLS_NUMERIC_CHARACTERS=",."') book_stipend
from rbrcomp
    left join (select *
                from 
                    (select 
                            :parm_aidy aidy_year,
                            'CH33' mil_ben,
                            '36M' service_code,
                            '36+ months: 100%' service_desc,
                            1 pct
                        from dual
                        union
                        select 
                            :parm_aidy aidy_year,
                            'CH33',
                            '30M',
                            '30 months: 90%',
                            .9 pct
                        from dual
                        union
                        select 
                            :parm_aidy aidy_year,
                            'CH33' mil_ben,
                            '24M',
                            '24 months: 80%',
                            .8 pct
                        from dual
                        union
                        select 
                            :parm_aidy aidy_year,
                            'CH33',
                            '18M',
                            '18 months: 70%',
                            .7 pct
                        from dual
                        union
                        select 
                            :parm_aidy aidy_year,
                            'CH33',
                            '6M',
                            '30 months: 60%',
                            .6 pct
                        from dual
                        union
                        select 
                            :parm_aidy aidy_year,
                            'CH33' mil_ben,
                            '90D',
                            '90 days: 50%',
                            .5 pct
                        from dual
                        union
                        select 
                            :parm_aidy aidy_year,
                            'CH33',
                            'GYSGT',
                            'GYSGT Fry Scholarship: 100%',
                            1 pct
                        from dual
                        union
                        select 
                            :parm_aidy aidy_year,
                            'CH33',
                            'SCD',
                            'Service-Connected Discharge: 100%',
                            1 pct
                        from dual
                        union
                        select
                            :parm_aidy aidy_year,
                            'CH33',
                            'PHS',
                            'Purple Heart Service: 100%',
                            1 pct
                        from dual
                        union
                        select
                            :parm_aidy aidy_year,
                            'CH30',
                            '3',
                            '3 or more years',
                            0 pct
                        from dual
                        union
                        select
                            :parm_aidy aidy_year,
                            'CH30',
                            '2',
                            '2 or more years',
                            0 pct
                        from dual
                        union
                        select
                            :parm_aidy aidy_year,
                            'CH1606',
                            '1',
                            'Select Reverve GI Bill (Chapter 1606)',
                            0 pct
                        from dual
                        union
                        select
                            :parm_aidy aidy_year,
                            'VRE',
                            '1' ,
                            'Veteran Readiness and Employment',
                            1 pct
                        from dual
                        union
                        select
                            :parm_aidy aidy_year,
                            'DEA',
                            '1' ,
                            'Dependents Educational Assistance (DEA)',
                            0 pct
                        from dual)
                        ) srv on srv.aidy_year = rbrcomp_aidy_code
where rbrcomp_aidy_code = :parm_aidy
    and mil_ben = :parm_mil_ben
    and rbrcomp_aprd_code = 'FASPR'
    and rbrcomp_comp_code = 'FEES'
    and rbrcomp_btyp_code = 'CAMP'
    and rbrcomp_bgrp_code = 'RAWH'
